articles.author: David Baratz
articles.title: See stunning images of 'Blood Moon' and total lunar eclipse - USA Today
articles.description: Stargazers enjoyed a "Blood Moon" overnight on September 7 during a total lunar eclipse visible across Asia and swathes of Europe and Africa.
